name: JF Projects
body:
# Welcome to JF Projects.
This is the main page of JF Projects. JF Projects are a set of different projects about OSGi, websockets, html5 and Java.

# JF Maven Repositories
All information regarding JF Maven Repositories can be found [here](https://github.com/jomarmar/jomarmar.github.io/wiki/JF-Maven-Repositories).

# Projects
The following is a list of the current projects:

## jf-parent
This project holds the common Maven configuration for all JF Projects (plugins configurations, dependencies, scm and distributionManagement...)
* [jf-parent (source)](https://github.com/jomarmar/jf-parent)
* [jf-parent (mvn-doc)](http://jomarmar.github.io/jf-parent/docs)

## jf-serializer
The aim of this project is to provide a Json serializer and parser for (almost) any Java Bean object.
* [jf-serializer (source)](https://github.com/jomarmar/jf-serializer)
* [jf-serializer (mvn-doc)](http://jomarmar.github.io/jf-serializer/docs/jf-serializer)

# Authors and Contributors
@jomarmar has been working on software development for 13 years and knows nothing yet. I will be glad to accept any contributions or suggestions for JF Projects.

# Support or Contact
Having trouble with JF Projects? Do you want to know more? Contact jomarmar@gmail.com.
